42
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:51,972
Bob also does the same.

43
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:57,410
They exchange the new colors.

44
00:03:59,980 --> 00:04:04,880
Now they mix the new colors with
their secret colors and produce yet

45
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:05,610
