46
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:14,350
Since the final color on each side is made
of the same combination of three colors,

47
00:04:14,350 --> 00:04:18,670
yellow, pink and green,
it is identical on both sides.

48
00:04:19,970 --> 00:04:24,908
So, Alice and Bob ended up with the same
final color without revealing their

49
00:04:24,908 --> 00:04:27,080
own secret colors to each other.

50
00:04:30,249 --> 00:04:35,470
As you can see on the screen,
the same thing happens mathematically.

51
00:04:36,650 --> 00:04:40,219
The final values computed on each
side are actually identical.

52
